# Project Management Tool

Welcome to the Project Management Tool repository! This tool is designed to simplify project management by providing an intuitive interface for tracking tasks, assigning IDs, and managing deadlines.

## Key Features

- Project Overview: Streamlined presentation of project details for enhanced clarity.
- Task Tracking: Effortlessly monitor project tasks with assigned task IDs.
- Task Assignment: Seamlessly assign tasks, complete with task IDs for clear identification.
- Project Naming: Personalize your projects by giving them unique and meaningful names.
- Mark as Completed: Easily track task progress by marking them as completed when done.
- Deadline Management: Stay organized with an intuitive interface to set and manage project deadlines.

## Technologies Used

- HTML: Crafted the structural foundation of the tool.
- CSS: Designed a visually appealing and user-friendly interface.
- JavaScript: Added dynamic elements for enhanced functionality.

